description:
CORPUS FAMILY MUTUAL FUND
Show Me the Body is a Queens based, New York Hardcore band. Corpus is their crew and collective, consisting of artists such as, TrippJones, Dreamcrusher, Dog Breath, Twisted Thing and more.
Corpus Public Radio is hosted by Noble Spell and Edited by Dre Betts.

CORPUS IS A COMMUNITY.
COMMUNITY BUILDING IS DIRECT ACTION.
CORPUS IS ABOUT MUTUAL RESPECT.
RESPECT BUILDS SOLIDARITY.
CORPUS IS BUILT ON HARD WORK AND PRACTICE.
INTELLECTUAL WARFARE IS MANDATORY.
INCREASING SELF DEFENSE AND AWARENESS IS PARAMOUNT.
CORPUS IS EMPOWERMENT AND BECOMING FREE.
